manifests.contents:
bench = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "zero2prod"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
required-features = []

[[test]]
path = "tests/health_check.rs"
name = "health_check"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "zero2prod"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[dependencies]
actix-web = "4"
serde = "1.0.115"
tracing = "0.1.19"
tracing-actix-web = "0.7"
tracing-bunyan-formatter = "0.3.1"
tracing-log = "0.1.1"

[dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4.22"
features = ["clock"]
default-features = false

[dependencies.config]
version = "0.13"
features = ["yaml"]
default-features = false

[dependencies.secrecy]
version = "0.8"
features = ["serde"]

[dependencies.sqlx]
version = "0.7"
features = ["runtime-tokio-rustls", "macros", "postgres", "uuid", "chrono", "migrate"]
default-features = false

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1"
features = ["macros", "rt-multi-thread"]

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3"
features = ["registry", "env-filter"]

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "1"
features = ["v4"]

[dev-dependencies]
once_cell = "1.7.2"

[dev-dependencies.reqwest]
version = "0.11"
features = ["json"]

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
required-features = []
